Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:24.50,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Now, wear this.}Tiếp theo là mang nó vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:29.41,Default,Myne,0,0,0,,{What is this, Head Priest?}Đây là gì ạ, thưa Cha?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:33.06,Default,F,0,0,0,,{Can't you tell? It's a magical item.}Là vật phẩm ma thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:39.61,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'm asking what we're using it for.}Con hỏi nó có tác dụng gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:44.68,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Please... tell... me...}Nói... con...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:52.62,Italics,F,0,0,0,,{Myne's the only one who uses \Nthis to tie her hair.}Myne là người duy nhất dùng thứ này để buộc tóc.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:54.33,Italics,F,0,0,0,,{And it's not just this hairpin.}Và nó không chỉ là buộc tóc bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:57.33,Italics,F,0,0,0,,{She has brought us all sorts of creations.}Con bé đã mang đến rất nhiều sự sáng tạo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:00:59.82,Italics,F,0,0,0,,{But the most surprising thing of all}Nhưng thứ ngạc nhiên nhất
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:02.17,Italics,F,0,0,0,,{is her passion for books.}là niềm đam mê của con bé với sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:09.21,Italics,F,0,0,0,,{She treasures literature, and even wrote\N some picture books for children.}Nó rất trân trọng văn học và đã viết một vài sách ảnh cho trẻ em.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:12.19,Italics,F,0,0,0,,{Her obsession is clearly abnormal.}Nhìn thế nào thì nó cũng thật kì lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:14.48,Italics,F,0,0,0,,{Just what goes through that head of yours?}Rốt cuộc con là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:22.75,Default,F,0,0,0,,{I shall take a look into your past, Myne.}Ta sẽ nhìn vào quá khứ của con, Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:34.59,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Before I was Myne,}Trước khi trở thành Myne,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:38.84,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I lived in a distant era as Motosu Urano.}tôi sống ở một thời đại xa xôi và tên là Motosu Urano.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.23,0:01:40.32,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Psychology.}Tâm lý học.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:41.41,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Religion.}Tôn giáo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:42.59,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{History.}Lịch sử.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:43.38,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Geography.}Địa lý.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:44.59,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Education.}Giáo dục.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:45.83,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Folklore.}Văn hóa dân gian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:46.94,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Mathematics.}Toán học.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:47.96,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Physics.}Vật lý.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:48.92,Italics,M,0,0,0,,Địa chất.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:49.97,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Chemistry.}Hóa học.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:51.14,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Biology.}Sinh học.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:52.28,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Art.}Nghệ thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:53.25,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Health.}Sức khỏe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:54.27,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Language.}Ngôn ngữ học.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:55.27,Default - Top,M,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Fiction...}{\i0}Tưởng tượng...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.73,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Literature was my life.}Tôi yêu quý sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:02:01.23,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I loved books—laden with mankind's knowledge\N in all disciplines—with all my heart,}Tôi yêu những cuốn sách chứa đầy kiến thức nhân loại.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:04.74,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{and felt unbridled joy at living \Na life surrounded by them.}Và cảm thấy sự hạnh phúc khi được vây quanh bởi sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:06.27,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{But then...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:13.57,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{On the verge of death, \NI uttered a silent prayer.}Trước cái chết, tôi thốt lên một lời cầu nguyện...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:19.53,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{"O God, may I be able to read all kinds\N of books in my next life, too."}"Chúa ơi, nếu có kiếp sau, con muốn được đọc tất cả các loại sách".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:44.10,Title,Title Card,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1)}{Ascendance of a Bookworm}Sự thống trị của mọt sách
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:55.00,Ep Title,Ep Title,0,0,0,,{Chapter One\N}{\fs24}{A World Without Books}Phần 1: Thế giới không có sách
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:04:01.04,Default,Myne,0,0,0,,{It's so hot... I can't breathe... \NI can't take this anymore!}Nóng quá... khó thở quá... Không chịu đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.15,Default,Motosu,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.42,Default,Myne,0,0,0,,{It's so hot... Help!}Nóng quá... Cứu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:05.71,Default,Motosu,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:08.17,Default,Myne,0,0,0,,{Someone help me!}Ai đó cứu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:09.82,Default,Mot,0,0,0,,{Huh? The voice is fading.}Ủa? Giọng nói đang nhỏ dần...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:11.10,Default,Mot,0,0,0,,{Wait!}Khoan đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:34.05,Default,Myne,0,0,0,,{Where am I?}Mình đang ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.46,Default,Myne,0,0,0,,{Are these really my hands?}Đây là tay mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:43.46,Default,Myne,0,0,0,,{Wait, I'm pretty sure I died.}Không đã? Hình như mình chết rồi mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:47.54,Default,Myne,0,0,0,,{Am I having some kind of weird, dying dream?}Hay mình đang mơ một giấc mơ kì lạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:55.73,Default,Myne,0,0,0,,{I'm not dreaming. What's going on?}Không phải mơ... Vậy là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.68,Default,Myne,0,0,0,,{What am I doing here?}Mình làm gì ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.12,Italics,Myne,0,0,0,,{Who is that?}Ai vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:03.70,Italics,Myne,0,0,0,,{Her hair's green!}Tóc xanh lá?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:10.02,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{What? I don't understand what she's saying.}Khoan... Mình không hiểu chị ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:16.58,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Someone's memories are \Nbursting into my mind!}Kí ức của ai đó đang tràn vào não mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:23.14,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.98,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{No! I'm not Myne!}Không! Tôi không phải Myne!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.89,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{My name is Motosu Urano!}Tên tôi là Motosu Urano!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:31.76,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Myne? Are you all right, Myne?}Myne? Con ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.15,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I can understand her now!}Mình có thể hiểu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:38.01,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{How are you feeling, Myne?}Con thấy sao, Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.13,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mom...}Mẹ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:44.95,Italics,Nar,0,0,0,,{In this moment, Motosu Urano \Nbegan her life as Myne.}Khoảnh khắc này, Motosu Urano đã trở thành Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:48.63,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{And that's when I realized...}Và đó là lúc mình nhận ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:53.41,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{My mother had been just as happy as me\Nwhen I landed my librarian job,}Mẹ rất vui khi mình tìm được một công việc thủ thư,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.54,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{but now I would never see her again.}nhưng mình sẽ không gặp lại bà ấy nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:00.21,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mom...}Mẹ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.29,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'm so sorry.}Con xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.18,Default,M,0,0,0,,{If only I had a book to read...}Nếu con có sách để đọc thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:12.75,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah, as long as I have books,}Phải, miễn là mình có sách,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:16.05,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I can deal with things no matter where I am.}thì dù thế nào vẫn sẽ cố chịu đựng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:18.78,Default,M,0,0,0,,{No. I }{\i1}{will}{\i0}{ deal with it.}Không, mình phải chịu được.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.11,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I just need my books.}Thế nên mình cần sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:25.33,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I wonder where I can find one, though...}Không biết sách ở đâu nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:29.88,Default,Turi,0,0,0,,{Myne? Are you okay to be up and about now?}Myne, em ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.73,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Turi, my older sister.}Chị Turi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:33.89,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Oh, I know.}Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:36.29,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Hey, Turi, bring me a book.}Nè Turi, mang sách cho em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.13,Default,T,0,0,0,,{A book?}Sách?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:40.57,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I wanna read.}Vâng, em muốn đọc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:43.33,Default,T,0,0,0,,{What's a book?}Sách là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.08,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:47.22,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Does she not know what a book is?}Chị ấy không biết về sách à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:51.20,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Hang on a sec. How does that even happen?}Khoan đã... Không biết là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:55.30,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Maybe there are no books \Nfor kids in this house?}Hay là nhà này không có sách?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:57.69,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Are you okay, Myne?}Em ổn chứ Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.69,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Myne, how's your fever?}Myne, con hạ sốt chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:04.30,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Mom, it looks like her head hurts.}Mẹ, em ấy có vẻ vẫn chưa khỏe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:11.49,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{The fever is starting to go down, but \NI guess you're still not feeling your best.}Cơn sốt đã hạ rồi nhưng có vẻ vẫn chưa khỏe lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:15.17,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Sleep tight until dinnertime, okay?}Con ngủ đến giờ ăn đi nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:16.70,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Come help me, Turi.}Turi, phụ mẹ nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.41,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Sure!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.24,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Now's my chance to find some books.}Giờ là lúc đi tìm sách!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:32.55,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Books are worth it.}Hi sinh vì sách!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.28,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Clothes, huh?}Quần áo à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What even is this?}Cái gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:50.99,Default,M,0,0,0,,{It would've been perfect if there \Nwere books in this very room,}Nếu phòng này có sách thì tốt... Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:53.16,Default,M,0,0,0,,{but I guess it's not gonna be that easy.}không dễ vậy đâu nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:56.32,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Time to check the next room over, then.}Qua phòng khác thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.70,Default,M,0,0,0,,{And we've already hit a snag.}Chưa gì đã tăng độ khó rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:23.48,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Whatever. Books are worth it.}Kệ, hi sinh vì sách!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.11,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I made it!}Tới rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.73,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Ow!}Đau!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:58.55,Default,M,0,0,0,,{This pain will be my medal of honor!}Đây là vết thương của sự tự hào!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.70,Default,M,0,0,0,,{It's open.}Nó mở rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.70,Default,M,0,0,0,,{The kitchen, huh?}Bếp à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:11.69,Default,M,0,0,0,,{No books in here, I bet.}Không có sách rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.51,Default,M,0,0,0,,{A storeroom, I think?}Phòng chứa đồ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:24.07,Default,M,0,0,0,,{It's locked. I wonder if it leads outside.}Nó bị khóa. Chắc là dẫn ra ngoài.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:28.51,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I looked all over the house, \Nbut I couldn't find any books.}Mình đã tìm khắp nơi mà không có sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:29.92,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:36.09,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Wait, are books really \Nexpensive in this world?}Hay sách ở thế giới này mắc?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.13,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Even in the history of my world,}Trong lịch sử của thế giới mình sống,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:43.67,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{books were rare and pricey till the printing \Npress made them possible to mass-produce.}sách rất hiếm và đắt tiền đến khi in ấn được phát minh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:48.60,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{If you weren't upper class, you would \Nnever get the chance to read one.}Nếu không phải tầng lớp quý tộc thì đừng hòng đụng vào sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.85,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Oh, well.}Chịu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:53.28,Default,M,0,0,0,,{There must be }{\i1}{something}{\i0}{ to read, though.}Nhưng phải có gì để đọc chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:57.87,Default,M,0,0,0,,{If not books, then newspapers or calendars.}Không phải sách thì báo hay lịch cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:09:59.60,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Nothing.}Không có.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:01.13,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Nothing.}Không luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:03.14,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Nothing.}Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:05.12,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Nothing.}Không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:09.11,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Nothing! Why is there no writing \Nin any way, shape, or form?}Không có gì cả? Tại sao không có một văn bản bằng chữ nào vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:13.62,Default,M,0,0,0,,{How the heck am I supposed to live here?}Mình sống nổi không đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.12,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{We're back.}Mẹ về rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:24.00,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Myne? Didn't I tell you to \Nstay in bed until dinnertime?}Myne? Mẹ bảo con ngủ đi mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:27.01,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{And look at this mess you've made.}Và nhìn con bới tung mọi thứ lên kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.38,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I can't find any books.}Không có sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:36.28,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{What's wrong, Myne?}Sao thế Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.90,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Does it hurt somewhere?}Đau đâu hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.59,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I can't find any books!}Con không thấy một cuốn sách nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.47,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I want a book!}Con muốn sách!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:53.43,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I want to read!}Con muốn đọc sách!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,{That's all I want!}Chỉ thế là đủ!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:59.42,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Who can I talk to that'll understand me?}Nè, ai có thể hiểu được con?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:01.92,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Someone please tell me!}Ai đó nói con nghe đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.94,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{It's been three days since I woke up as Myne.}Đã 3 ngày mình sống dưới cái tên Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:19.57,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{These three days have been hell.}Đã 3 ngày sống trong địa ngục.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:23.95,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Also, life here seriously sucks.}Cơ mà cuộc sống ở đây cũng thật tồi tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:27.08,Default,M,0,0,0,,{The "toilet" is a bedroom bedpan \Nwhich is then dumped outside,}Đi vệ sinh ngay cạnh giường ngủ và đổ thẳng ra ngoài.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:31.58,Default,M,0,0,0,,{and then "Dad," who I barely \Neven know, changes my clothes.}Và còn bị ba ép thay đồ nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.05,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Good grief!}Thiệt tình mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:37.96,sign_16456_150_Femininity,SignL,0,0,0,,{Femininity}Nữ tính
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:37.96,sign_16456_151_Shame,SignR,0,0,0,,{Shame}Xấu hổ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.59,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I have to abandon these \Nthings or I'll never last!}Mình phải dẹp bỏ hết mấy chuyện này nếu muốn sống!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:45.72,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Now I've given up and even \Nget them to wipe me down.}Mình đã từ bỏ và để họ thoải mái lau người.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:49.64,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Turi thought that was weird, \Nbut it made me feel a lot better.}Turi nghĩ mình kì lạ nhưng con bé làm mình thấy ổn hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.19,Default,M,0,0,0,,{And then...}Và...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.06,Flashback,T,0,0,0,,{What are you doing?}Em làm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:55.98,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{I'm trying to tie up my hair \N'cause it's bothering me,}Buộc tóc, tóc dài vướng víu quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.94,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{but it's not working out.}Nhưng mà cũng không khá hơn chút nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.57,Flashback,T,0,0,0,,{Well, you do have really straight hair.}Tại tóc em thẳng mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:03.32,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah. If I use a ribbon, it falls right away.}Ừm, nếu xài ruy băng thì nó tuột ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.41,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{Oh, right.}Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.29,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{Can I break this?}Em bẻ cái này nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.41,Flashback,T,0,0,0,,{That's my doll!}Đó là búp bê của chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:14.04,Flashback,T,0,0,0,,{You know it's important to me! You meanie!}Là báu vật của chị đó! Em ác quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.21,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{Uh, sorry.}Xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:19.92,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{I want a hairpin... I guess you \Nwouldn't know what I mean.}Tại em muốn làm cái kẹp tóc... À mà chắc chị cũng không hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:24.30,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{I need a thin wooden stick \Nlike this doll's legs.}Em cần một thanh gỗ mỏng như chân con búp bê này.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:28.68,Flashback,T,0,0,0,,{In that case, I could make one for you.}Thế thì chị làm cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:33.48,Flashback,T,0,0,0,,{Will this do?}Thế này hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:36.06,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah! Thanks, Turi!}A, cảm ơn Turi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.19,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{How does that look?}Thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.19,Flashback,T,0,0,0,,{Myne, no!}Không được đâu Myne!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:44.95,Flashback,T,0,0,0,,{Only grown-ups are allowed \Nto tie all their hair up.}Chỉ người lớn mới để tóc lên cao thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.82,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{Really?}Thật à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.37,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{Is this okay, then?}Thế này thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.66,Flashback,T,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I think so.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:57.29,Flashback,T,0,0,0,,{But from here it looks like you've \Ngot a splinter stuck in your head.}Nhưng giống như em có một cái que xuyên qua đầu vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.79,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{Oh, that's fine.}À, không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:04.01,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Now what do I do about my hair? \NIt feels so sticky and gross.}Tóc mấy ngày không gội rồi nên bết quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.01,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{How are you feeling, Myne?}Sao rồi Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:11.02,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Your fever's gone. Do you feel tired?}Con hạ sốt rồi nhỉ? Còn mệt không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:11.89,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Nope.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:15.64,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Do you want to go shopping with Mom, then?}Con muốn đi mua sắm cùng mẹ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.23,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Shopping?}Mua sắm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:22.90,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I didn't find any books at home, \Nbut there might be a bookstore out there.}Mình không tìm thấy sách trong nhà, có khi ở ngoài sẽ có hiệu sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.86,Default,M,0,0,0,,{If there is one...}Nếu có thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.95,Default,M,0,0,0,,{"I won't feel lonely if I have books.}"Nếu có sách thì con sẽ hết buồn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.66,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll watch over the house all you want!"}Và sẽ trông nhà cẩn thận hơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.91,Default,M,0,0,0,,{That should get her to buy me some!}Mẹ nên mua cho con vài cuốn!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:34.41,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yep! I wanna go!}Vâng! Con muốn đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.37,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Oh? Where is all this energy coming from?}Ủa? Sao tự nhiên khỏe lên thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:39.67,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I know it'll be fun!}Vì chắc sẽ vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:43.01,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Let's go shopping, then.}Vậy đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.85,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Cold! Scary! Stinky!}Lạnh! Tối! Hôi nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.27,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Get on, Myne.}Lên đây nào Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:58.31,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{You can't walk all the way to \Nthe market, right? Come on.}Con đâu thể tự mình đến chợ được nhỉ? Đi nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:00.11,Default,M,0,0,0,,{O-Okay...}V-Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:04.78,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I see.}Ra là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:08.99,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Myne's body is pretty frail, so Mom's \Nalways given her piggyback rides.}Cơ thể của Myne lúc nào cũng yếu nên luôn được cõng đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:12.95,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{But I'm pretty sure I could \Nhandle this easily.}Nhưng nếu chỉ thế này thì mình dư sức.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:20.25,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Our building has five floors, huh?}Nhà mình có 5 tầng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:27.26,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Wow, this area's full of townhouses.}Khu này toàn nhà phố.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:32.51,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{So that's where we get the water from.}Chỗ kia để lấy nước nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:08.72,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Amazing! It's like a Medieval European town \Nstraight out of all those photobooks!}Tuyệt quá! Cứ như mấy thị trấn Châu Âu thời trung cổ ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:11.30,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mom, is that a castle?}Mẹ, đó là tòa thành hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.64,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{It's the cathedral.}Là nhà thờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:16.27,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{When you turn seven, you'll get \Nto go there for your baptism.}Khi nào lên 7, con sẽ đến đó làm lễ rửa tội.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:17.73,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Huh...}Hừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:24.06,Default,M,0,0,0,,{That's an awfully big gate.}Cánh cổng to quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.73,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{That's the castle town gate.}Đó là cổng thành.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:31.16,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Beyond it lies the lord's castle \Nand the other nobility's mansions,}Bên ngoài là lâu đài lãnh chúa và giới quý tộc,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:33.74,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{but it's kind of a different world to us.}một thế giới khác với chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.53,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What about that wall?}Còn bức tường kia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:38.70,Default,M,0,0,0,,{The city wall. It keeps us safe inside.}Đó là tường thành, nó bảo vệ chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:41.25,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Dad's a gatekeeper at\N the south gate, remember?}Ba là lính giữ cổng ở phía Nam đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.67,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Oh, right.}À phải...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.51,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Gatekeeper, yeah...}Lính giữ cổng nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:55.72,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{But if there's a lord's castle, \Nand it's surrounded by walls,}Nhưng nếu có lâu đài lãnh chúa và được bao quanh bởi bờ tường,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.52,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{then that means this is \Ntechnically a big city.}vậy đây là thành phố lớn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.52,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{And yet,}Vậy mà,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.94,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I don't see any writing \Nanywhere in town, either.}mình chẳng thấy biểu tượng đó đâu cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:08.90,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Do they not have a writing system at all?}Họ không có hệ thống chữ viết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.28,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{The thought didn't even cross my mind!}Mình không muốn chuyện đó là thật đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:14.03,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{We've reached the market, Myne.}Đến chợ rồi đó, Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.62,Default,W,0,0,0,,{Can I have three of these?}Lấy tôi ba củ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.62,Default,G,0,0,0,,Có ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:18.87,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{Hurry up!}Nhanh lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:20.12,Default - Top,G,0,0,0,,{Fresh seasonal vegetables. \NWould you like to try any?}Rau tươi đây! Mại dô!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:31.22,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I hadn't even considered that they \Nmight not have a writing system.}Mình không nghĩ là họ không có chữ viết...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:35.84,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{If that's true, then they're \Nnot gonna have any books!}Nhưng nếu không có thật thì sẽ chẳng có sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:42.60,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mom! What's that on that plank?}Mẹ! Tấm ván đó viết gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:48.07,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Oh, it shows the price, so you know \Nhow much you can buy something for.}À, giá tiền đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:51.07,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Numbers! They do have a number system!}Là chữ số! Họ có hệ thống chữ số!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.78,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What does it say, Mom?}Nó viết gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.99,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{This is 20 lyon,}20 lyon,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:58.08,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{and that's 23 lyon.}bên kia là 23 lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.70,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Is this 30 lyon, then?}Vậy đây là 30 lyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.37,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{That's correct!}Chính xác!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:05.87,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{I can't believe you picked it up so \Nquickly. You're very smart, Myne.}Con học nhanh thật đó Myne!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:10.17,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What is this stench?}Mùi gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.97,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Myne? What's wrong?}Sao thế Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:22.31,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Dead chicken!}Gà...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:35.45,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Myne? Hang in there, Myne!}Myne! Tỉnh dậy đi, Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:38.95,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mom...}Mẹ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:42.24,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{You fainted all of a sudden.\N I didn't know what to do.}Tự nhiên con bất tỉnh làm mẹ lo lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:43.58,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Are you okay now?}Giờ ổn chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:47.00,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'm... not okay.}Không... ổn lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:48.75,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Oh...}Vậy à...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:52.25,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Oh, dear. I can't get any \Nshopping done like this.}Chết thật... Thế này sao mua sắm được.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:55.30,Default,M,0,0,0,,Mẹ cứ đi đi, con ngồi đây chờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:56.76,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:01.76,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Ma'am.}Cô ơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:06.10,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Do you mind if I wait here for a while,\Nplease? I'm not feeling very well.}Cháu cảm thấy không khỏe nên ngồi đây nghỉ chút được không ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.60,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I promise I won't be any trouble.}Cháu sẽ không gây phiền phức đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:13.07,Default,W,0,0,0,,{Oh, my. Aren't you a polite young lady?}Chà chà, cô bé thật lễ phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:16.03,Default,W,0,0,0,,{No problem. Go get your shopping done.}Không sao. Chị cứ đi mua sắm đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:18.45,Default,W,0,0,0,,{You don't want her fainting again, do you?}Con bé mà ngất nữa thì mệt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:21.66,Default,G,0,0,0,,{If you're worried, she can \Nwait inside the shop.}Nếu lo thì cứ vào trong quán mà nghỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:25.37,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Nobody's going to kidnap her\Nif she's in the back.}Không ai dám bắt cóc con bé nếu nó vào đây đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.54,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll be a good girl and wait.}Con sẽ ngoan mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:30.50,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Thank you so much. I'll be right back.}Cảm ơn hai người, tôi sẽ quay lại ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.29,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Stay right here, okay?}Ngoan đấy nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:32.84,Default,M,0,0,0,,{'Kay.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.17,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Please take care of her.}Nhờ anh chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:38.01,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{It's all too much for me to take in.}Mình diễn giỏi quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:42.93,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Thanks for having me.}Cháu xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:56.49,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Wait, could that be...}Khoan... đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:02.20,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mister! What... What is that?!}Chú ơi! Đó là gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.99,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Oh, it's a book.}À, là sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.41,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yahoo!}Tuyệt vời!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.04,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I finally found one!}Cuối cùng cũng thấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.00,Default,M,0,0,0,,{There }{\i1}{are}{\i0}{ books here!}Có sách kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:15.00,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Is this your first time seeing one?}Cháu mới thấy lần đầu à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.05,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:20.76,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Hey, do you know a shop that \Nsells books? Where is it?}Nè, cửa hàng bán sách ở đâu vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:24.01,Default,G,0,0,0,,{A shop? There isn't one.}Cửa hàng? Không có đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:27.89,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Huh? There are books, but no bookstores?}Hả? Có sách nhưng không có cửa hàng bán?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:31.85,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Books have to be copied by hand, you see.}Sách phải viết bằng tay mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:35.82,Default,G,0,0,0,,{They cost so much money that \Nvery few people can buy any.}Giá nó rất cao nên ít người mua lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:40.61,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Even this one was pawned off by \Na noble who couldn't repay his debt.}Cuốn này là từ một quý tộc bị vỡ nợ bán lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:42.45,Default,G,0,0,0,,{I haven't put it on sale.}Ta vẫn chưa thể bán cho ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:46.91,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Only other nobles would even think \Nabout buying something so expensive.}Chỉ những quý tộc khác may ra mới có tiền mua nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:51.21,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Damn those lucky nobles!}Lũ quý tộc chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.46,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{In that case...}Nếu thế thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:57.34,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Please let me hold that book!}Hãy cho cháu sờ thử nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:58.09,sign_28395_285_Kowtow__In_Japan,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fnArial\b1\pos(115,250)\bord0}{Kowtow\N}{\fs12\fscx95}{ In Japan, this is the most dramatic \Nshow of requesting or apologizing}Dogeza: Quỳ thành kính
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:01.26,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I know I can't buy it, so I'll \Nmake do with just holding it!}Cháu không có tiền mua nó nên chỉ cần cầm thử thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:03.93,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'd like to at least enjoy \Nthe sweet scent of ink!}Ít nhất hãy cho cháu ngửi mùi mực!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:05.22,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I beg you!}Xin chú!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:13.23,Default,G,0,0,0,,{I don't know why, but I get the feeling \Nthat it'd be risky to let you touch it.}Ta không biết sao... Nhưng cảm giác cho cháu sờ vào sẽ nguy hiểm lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.57,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Please wait.}Khoan đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:19.28,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll just flip through it, I promise.}Cháu chỉ nhìn lướt qua thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.07,Default,G,0,0,0,,{No.}Không được.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.28,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I understand.}Vậy ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:30.12,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Thank you for looking after my daughter.}Cảm ơn vì đã chăm sóc con bé.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.08,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Okay, Myne. Let's go home.}Về thôi Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:35.67,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I didn't even get to hold it.}Mình vẫn chẳng thể sờ vào nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:46.97,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{I got some raffle fruit, your favorite.}Mẹ có mua ít trái cây con thích nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.01,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:49.81,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,{Are you still not feeling well?}Vẫn còn mệt hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.72,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:55.81,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{There are no bookstores in this town.}Ở đây không có hiệu sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:21:01.11,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{In fact, there might be not be \Nany anywhere in this world.}Có thể là trên toàn thế giới...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:15.46,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I'm not gonna get any books \Nif there are no bookstores.}Mình sẽ không có sách nếu không có cửa hàng sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:16.92,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{What can I do, then?}Làm gì bây giờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:19.96,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll just have to make them myself!}Thế thì tự làm cho rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:22.92,Default,T,0,0,0,,Tự làm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.34,Default,Eva,0,0,0,,Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.93,Default,Gunter,0,0,0,,{What are you going to make?}Con định làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:27.97,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Nothing. Never mind.}Không có gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.43,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Forget it. I don't care what it takes.}Không còn cách nào khác!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:35.44,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna get my books if \Nit's the last thing I do!}Mình sẽ bằng mọi cách để có sách!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:37.44,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I won't let this world beat me!}Không thể chịu thua được!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:14.41,sign_33349_312_Next_Chapter_Lif,,0,0,0,,{Next Chapter\N}{\fs24}{Lifestyle Upgrades and Slates}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{I see.}Ra là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{So your obsession for books\Nremained with you even after death.}Tức là sự cuồng sách của con vẫn không mất sau khi chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is making my head hurt.}Ta hơi đau đầu rồi đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.26,0:23:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Please don't say that with a straight face.}Cha đừng nói thẳng thừng thế chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.62,0:23:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{You don't even get to show up until—}Cha cũng không cần xuất hiện đến khi--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{No spoilers, fool!}Cấm spoiler, con nhỏ ngốc!
